{"tid":2314432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠三個星期就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-06T14:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T07:01:11.000Z","uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa96fe14332b3196e3298cba997d5c893d62a5c","tid":2314432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0e6653df65754f5d1da993e99efec44f3c5bdd","tid":2314432,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"本na留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fef33d41d0e4a83e735494594c4fd0753f72d46","tid":2314432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a0e6653df65754f5d1da993e99efec44f3c5bdd","tid":2314432,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"本na留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"nana早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e21b6cf68c42570f2a625150818907039c25f8","tid":2314432,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"Save12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded241203ebc18bef511853d8514bddd1d244471","tid":2314432,"u